name: I'm a paper plane
description:
Enjoy being a paper plane and aviod hitting balloons, being caught by birds or... Wait, being abducted by aliens?

In this funny game your objective is to beat your own score. It's created for the weekly game jam, week 167. It's been made in a week so i hope you enjoy this little project.

If you fall fast you won't be able to react if an enemy tries to kill you, so play smart and survive as much as you can.
